settings.data:
Looking forward to seeing everyone for another killer weekend in Austin, Texas!

If you have any issues using the ticket links below you can visit THIS PAGE


VIEW SCHEDULE & SET TIMES

settings.text3:
Our festival format is a series of shows in downtown Austin, held across multiple venues within walking distance from each other.
* please note that due to a fire at Parish, we have had to move some shows to new venues as of 10/26 that are outside this area*

Grab tickets to each show below or choose from two Pass options.
If you're not sure which to get, check out more info here: PASS INFO

Buy Tickets on Eventbrite
Choose from General Admission or Deluxe:

GENERAL ADMISSION - SOLD OUT

Tickets to all 4 events at STUBBS during LEVITATION, OCT 27-30, 2022:

10/27 - THE JESUS AND MARY CHAIN + MORE

10/28 - KING GIZZARD AND THE LIZARD WIZARD + MORE

10/29 - KING GIZZARD & THE LIZARD WIZARD + MORE

10/30 - THE BLACK ANGELS + MORE

DELUXE - $485

All access above plus Deluxe Tickets at Stubbs:

– Access to exclusive lounge, private bar & elevated viewing platform at rear of venue
– Access to viewing area by front of venue (limited space available)
– Private bathrooms
– Express entry
– Complimentary food & non-alcoholic drinks

Choose from General Admission or Deluxe:
